Detailed Description

A Dictionary of string to List of strings (Dictionary< String, List< String > >).

An AttributesDictionary is used to define protection key attributes. For example, when creating a key with Agent::CreateKeys(), attributes can be provided to the keys being created. The attributes used (if any) when creating a key will also be given back when retrieving the keys via Agent::GetKeys().
